    <title>Easy Hiking Breakfast </title>

    <comment></comment>
    <thumbnail>../images/placeholder.png</thumbnail>
    <image></image>
    <category></category>
    <yield></yield>
    <prepTime></prepTime>
    <cookTime></cookTime>
    



    <ingredient>1 small ziplock bag</ingredient>
    <ingredient>2 Wheatbix</ingredient>
    <ingredient>2 TBsp powered full cream milk</ingredient>
    <ingredient>2 teasp sugar</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1/4 cup water ( added at camp site)</ingredient>

    <step>
Add to the ziplock bag wheatbix, powdered milk and sugar. Bring one for each morning for your hike. Add 1/4 cup water directly to the bag and massage to mix. Eat directly out of the bag.
    </step>
</recipe>